HEADWORD: indoleacetic acid
<hw>in"dole*a*cet"ic ac"id</hw> <pr>(⟦icr⟧n"d⟦omac⟧l)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem., Bot.)</fld> <def>A plant hormone
